] = status of the action on the file.&#10;    $p_info['crc'] = CRC of the file content.&#10;Parameters :&#10;Return Values :&#10;--------------------------------------------------------------------------------" ilk="function" line="3234" lineend="3254" name="privConvertHeader2FileInfo" returns="v_result" signature="privConvertHeader2FileInfo($p_header, &amp; $p_info)"><variable ilk="argument" line="3234" name="p_header" /><variable ilk="argument" line="3234" name="p_info" /><variable citdl="PclZipUtilPathReduction()" line="3239" name="v_temp_path" /><variable citdl="int" line="3236" name="v_result" /></scope><scope doc="--------------------------------------------------------------------------------&#10;Function : privExtractByRule()&#10;Description :&#10;  Extract a file or directory depending of rules (by index, by name, ...)&#10;Parameters :&#10;  $p_file_list : An array where will be placed the properties of each&#10;                 extracted file&#10;  $p_path : Path to add while writing the extracted files&#10;  $p_remove_path : Path to remove (from the file memorized path) while writing the&#10;                   extracted files. If the path does not match the file path,&#10;                   the file is extracted with its memorized path.&#10;                   $p_remove_path does not apply to 'list' mode.&#10;                   $p_path and $p_remove_path are commulative.&#10;Return Values :&#10;  1 on success,0 or less on error (see error code list)&#10;--------------------------------------------------------------------------------" ilk="function" line="3273" lineend="3601" name="privExtractByRule" returns="v_result" signature="privExtractByRule(&amp; $p_file_list, $p_path, $p_remove_path, $p_remove_all_path, &amp; $p_options)"><variable ilk="argument" line="3273" name="p_file_list" /><variable ilk="argument" line="3273" name="p_path" /><variable ilk="argument" line="3273" name="p_remove_path" /><variable ilk="argument" line="3273" name="p_remove_all_path